9. DATABASE SCHEMA REVIEW
================================================================================

GOOD:
  - Foreign keys with cascadeOnDelete / nullOnDelete
  - Soft deletes on critical entities
  - Unique constraints on (student, date), (certification, student), etc.
  - Composite indexes for search columns
  - Migrations use hasTable()/hasColumn() guards

ISSUES:
  - Missing indexes on invoices.status, payments.status, internships.status
  - achievements.department_id is string instead of FK
  - teacher_id in schedules initially added without FK (later migration tries fix)

